      Developer ID (non-sandboxed) distribution with Hardened Runtime enabled.
      PowerSnek needs no special entitlements: overlay windows, IOKit power-source
      reads, and SMAppService login-item registration all work under a standard
      hardened-runtime signature. Declare any future runtime exceptions here.
